WEBVTT

00:00:01.397 --> 00:00:04.119
So our story started several years ago,

00:00:04.143 --> 00:00:06.635
when my wife and I
got a complaint letter in the mail

00:00:06.659 --> 00:00:08.698
from an anonymous neighbor.

00:00:09.485 --> 00:00:11.131
(Laughter)

00:00:11.155 --> 00:00:15.839
I'll never forget the way
my wife transformed before my eyes

00:00:15.863 --> 00:00:19.603
from this graceful, peaceful, sweet woman

00:00:19.627 --> 00:00:24.564
into just an angry mother grizzly bear
whose cubs needed to be protected.

00:00:24.588 --> 00:00:26.175
It was intense.

00:00:26.675 --> 00:00:28.342
So here's what happened.

00:00:28.366 --> 00:00:29.656
This is our family.

00:00:29.680 --> 00:00:32.566
This is my wife and I
and our five awesome kids.